                <head>59. Summary of Conclusions of a Special Coordination Committee Meeting<note
                        n="1" type="source" xml:id="d59fn1">Source: Carter Library, National
                        Security Council, <gloss target="#t_NSC_1">NSC</gloss> Institutional Files
                        (H–Files), Box 106, <gloss target="#t_SCC_1">SCC</gloss> 210 Iran 11/26/79.
                        Top Secret. The meeting took place in the White House Situation Room.
                            <persName corresp="#p_CJ_1">Carter</persName> wrote “Zbig, J” in the
                        upper right corner.</note>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>Washington</placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian"
                            from="1979-11-26T09:15:00-05:00" to="1979-11-26T10:50:00-05:00">November
                            26, 1979, 9:15–10:50 a.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <list type="subject">
                    <head>SUBJECT</head>
                    <item>Iran</item>
                </list>
                <list type="participants">
                    <head>PARTICIPANTS</head>
                    <item>The Vice President</item>
